11#include "pc/sctp_data_channel_transport.h"
12
13#include "absl/types/optional.h"
14#include "pc/sctp_utils.h"
15
16namespace webrtc {
17
18SctpDataChannelTransport::SctpDataChannelTransport(
19 cricket::SctpTransportInternal* sctp_transport)
20 : sctp_transport_(sctp_transport) {
21 sctp_transport_->SignalReadyToSendData.connect(
22 this, &SctpDataChannelTransport::OnReadyToSendData);
23 sctp_transport_->SignalDataReceived.connect(
24 this, &SctpDataChannelTransport::OnDataReceived);
25 sctp_transport_->SignalClosingProcedureStartedRemotely.connect(
26 this, &SctpDataChannelTransport::OnClosingProcedureStartedRemotely);
27 sctp_transport_->SignalClosingProcedureComplete.connect(
28 this, &SctpDataChannelTransport::OnClosingProcedureComplete);
29 sctp_transport_->SignalClosedAbruptly.connect(
30 this, &SctpDataChannelTransport::OnClosedAbruptly);
31}
32
33RTCError SctpDataChannelTransport::OpenChannel(int channel_id) {
34 sctp_transport_->OpenStream(channel_id);
35 return RTCError::OK();
36}
37
38RTCError SctpDataChannelTransport::SendData(
39 int channel_id,
40 const SendDataParams& params,
41 const rtc::CopyOnWriteBuffer& buffer) {
42 cricket::SendDataResult result;
43 sctp_transport_->SendData(channel_id, params, buffer, &result);
44
45 // TODO(mellem): See about changing the interfaces to not require mapping
46 // SendDataResult to RTCError and back again.
47 switch (result) {
48 case cricket::SendDataResult::SDR_SUCCESS:
49 return RTCError::OK();
50 case cricket::SendDataResult::SDR_BLOCK: {
51 // Send buffer is full.
52 ready_to_send_ = false;
53 return RTCError(RTCErrorType::RESOURCE_EXHAUSTED);
54 }
55 case cricket::SendDataResult::SDR_ERROR:
56 return RTCError(RTCErrorType::NETWORK_ERROR);
57 }
58 return RTCError(RTCErrorType::NETWORK_ERROR);
59}
60
61RTCError SctpDataChannelTransport::CloseChannel(int channel_id) {
62 sctp_transport_->ResetStream(channel_id);
63 return RTCError::OK();
64}
65
66void SctpDataChannelTransport::SetDataSink(DataChannelSink* sink) {
67 sink_ = sink;
68 if (sink_ && ready_to_send_) {
69 sink_->OnReadyToSend();
70 }
71}
72
73bool SctpDataChannelTransport::IsReadyToSend() const {
74 return ready_to_send_;
75}
76
77void SctpDataChannelTransport::OnReadyToSendData() {
78 ready_to_send_ = true;
79 if (sink_) {
80 sink_->OnReadyToSend();
81 }
82}
83
84void SctpDataChannelTransport::OnDataReceived(
85 const cricket::ReceiveDataParams& params,
86 const rtc::CopyOnWriteBuffer& buffer) {
87 if (sink_) {
88 sink_->OnDataReceived(params.sid, params.type, buffer);
89 }
90}
91
92void SctpDataChannelTransport::OnClosingProcedureStartedRemotely(
93 int channel_id) {
94 if (sink_) {
95 sink_->OnChannelClosing(channel_id);
96 }
97}
98
99void SctpDataChannelTransport::OnClosingProcedureComplete(int channel_id) {
100 if (sink_) {
101 sink_->OnChannelClosed(channel_id);
102 }
103}
104
105void SctpDataChannelTransport::OnClosedAbruptly() {
106 if (sink_) {
107 sink_->OnTransportClosed();
108 }
109}
110
111} // namespace webrtc
